  <variables>
    <variable name="INPUT_FILE_FROM_USER_SPACE" value="" model="PA:USER_FILE" description="A file to select in the &lt;b&gt;User Data Space&lt;/b&gt;"   />
    <variable name="INPUT_FILE_FROM_GLOBAL_SPACE" value="" model="PA:GLOBAL_FILE" description="A file to select in the &lt;b&gt;Global Data Space&lt;/b&gt;"   />
  </variables>
  <description>
    <![CDATA[ A workflow that allows to upload a global file and a user file, then show its contents as job result. Specifically, the workflow takes a `PA:GLOBAL_FILE` variable and an `PA:USER_FILE` variable as the inputs. For each variable of these two types, at submission the File Browser will be shown. It allows the user to upload one or several files on its Global / User Data Spaces, and to select one file as the variable value for submission. ]]>
  </description>
